            .col-md-6.banner-image.wow.fadeInUp{"data-wow-duration" => "1.2s"}
              %img.featurespc{:alt => "", :src => asset_path("full-width-images/pc1.png"), :style => ""}/
            %h1.marginbo REVERSE AUCTION
            %p.tit1 Ensure affordability and efficiency with our Reverse Auction approach. When the roles of buyer and seller are flipped, healthy competition ensures fair market value. 
          #POTENTIAL.tab-pane.fade
            .col-md-6.banner-image
              %img.featurespc{:alt => "", :src => asset_path("full-width-images/pc2.png"), :style => ""}/
            %h1.marginbo AUTOMATED SALES LEADS
            %p.tit1 As users search for parts, vendors with the appropriate part are notified of the sale opportunity, which reduces time spent searching for leads and provides vendors with a larger reach of customers.
          #SECURE.tab-pane.fade
            .col-md-6.banner-image
              %img.featurespc{:alt => "", :src => asset_path("full-width-images/pc3.png"), :style => ""}/
            %h1.marginbo SECURE PAYMENT
            %p.tit1 Protecting both buyers and vendors is our priority. Every payment is transferred into escrow prior to shipment to ensure that the seller will receive payment. This safeguard also protects the buyer since they must approve the delivery for payment to be released from the escrow account. All disputes are handled by a third party, NetNeutrals.com.
          #INVENTORY.tab-pane.fade
            .col-md-6.banner-image
              %img.featurespc{:alt => "", :src => asset_path("full-width-images/pc4.png"), :style => ""}/
            %h1.marginbo INVENTORY LISTING
            %p.tit1 Our platform allows you to list all your parts using an excel spreadsheet. Once the parts are uploaded, users can attach traceability documents to each part to accelerate the bidding process. 
          #ASSET.tab-pane.fade
            .col-md-6.banner-image
              %img.featurespc{:alt => "", :src => asset_path("full-width-images/pc5.png"), :style => ""}/
            %h1.marginbo ASSET LISTING
            %p.tit1 Listing an Aircraft or Engine for sale or lease has never been easier. Market any available asset for free on Bid Aero. This free, online resource allows the user to upload documents on each individual aircraft and engine available for sale or for lease to provide all the information needed to interested parties. 
          #FINANCIAL.tab-pane.fade
            .col-md-6.banner-image
